Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The World Series gets the vote, 1980
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w54h
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Oct 1980
The World Series gets the popular vote while the presidential candidates get mean with each other. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less